<h2>Conversion rate benchmarks for Google Ads</h2>
<p><strong>The <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/2025-google-ads-benchmarks" target="_blank" rel="noopener">average conversion rate across Google Ads</a> is 7.52%.Â </strong></p>
