<div><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/2025-GA-Benchmarks-CVR-871x1024.webp" alt="2025 google ads benchmarks - conversion rate chart year over year" width="871" height="1024" class="aligncenter wp-image-91513 size-large" /></div>
