<h2>What is a call to action in marketing?</h2>
<p>In marketing, a <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2016/03/07/call-to-action-marketing">call to action</a>, or CTA, is a word or phrase that tells your <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2014/09/18/beginners-guide-to-target-markets">target audience</a> what to do next. They can be plain copy, but theyâ€™re often clickable links either in text or in a <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2015/02/20/call-to-action-buttons">CTA button</a>.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/call-to-action-example-barkbright.jpg" alt="call to action - screenshot of a landing page from brand Bark Bright" width="923" height="348" class="aligncenter wp-image-76600 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/call-to-action-example-barkbright.jpg 923w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/call-to-action-example-barkbright-480x181.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 923px, 100vw" /></p>
<p>You can use CTAs in just about any type of marketing message. In fact, a customer might see several CTAs as they move from unaware prospect to repeat buyer.</p>
<p>For example, someone might click a â€œlearn moreâ€ button on your Facebook ad, then click a â€œsubscribe nowâ€ button on your landing page, then click a â€œbuy nowâ€ CTA button from your newsletter.</p>
<p><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/16.0.1/72x72/1f6a8.png" alt="ðŸš¨" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> Boring CTAs wonâ€™t cut it. Download this free guide of <a href="https://marketing.wordstream.com/WSLIQContentDLWebsite36CallToActionPhrases.html?cid=Web_Any_InContentTextLink_36CallToActionPhrases_Download">the 36 best call-to-action phrases ever</a> and start using conversion-boosting CTAs.</p>
<div id="benefits-of-a-call-to-action"></div>
<h2>Benefits of a good call to action</h2>
<p>A call to action is a signpost that leads people down the road of becoming a customer. It helps to keep prospects moving toward that goal so they donâ€™t veer off and get distracted.</p>
<p>These examples show the influence of a great call to action:</p>
<ul>
<li>Emails with a single CTA increased clicks by <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2015/06/10/digital-marketing-stats">371%</a> and sales by 1617%.</li>
