<p>For the sake of this article, weâ€™re going to refer to all of those actions as conversions. And the goal of increasing our conversion performance can be greatly impacted by increasing conversion rates.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/average-search-advertising-conversion-rates.jpg" alt="average search advertising conversion rate by industry from wordstream google ads benchmarks report" width="712" height="599" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-75892" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/average-search-advertising-conversion-rates.jpg 712w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/average-search-advertising-conversion-rates-480x404.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 712px, 100vw" /></p>
