<p>If youâ€™re unsure of how fast your pages are loading or not sure what to do to make them run more quickly, you can use <a href="https://pagespeed.web.dev/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Googleâ€™s PageSpeed Insights</a> tool to get a handle on both of those things.</p>
